name: WELCOME TO 2049
description:
WELCOME TO 2049 is a photo art inspired by the movie blade runner 2049, I recreated the famous blade runner movie look in this masterpiece and am also giving away the lightroom lut(settings) too that I used in recreating the look to the people who are going to buy this art. If you are a blade runner lover then add this piece to your collection and get the lut too so you can create more pieces like this on your own.
Am going to release 21 editions of this NFT and here is my Twitter handle(@TusharNaruka) after purchasing this NFT drop me a text on Twitter so I can send you the blade runner lut :)
